  <description><![CDATA[<p>This is a beautifully decorated hotel and and a good choice for families. Your hosts are the Baud family who pride themselves on friendly service and the wonderful food that is served here. The spa area and heated indoor/outdoor pool provide the idea place to relax after a day on the piste. Or simply enjoy an après-ski drink in the cosy bar before sampling the excellent food. The hotel is 400m to the nearest lift and for your convenience the hotel offers a minibus shuttle service all day. The free resort bus also stops just outside the door and runs every 10 minutes.</p>]]></description>
