  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking), bath with hand held shower head attachment or shower room, WC, cable / satellite TV with English speaking channels, towels, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, WiFi, safety deposit box, bath robes, hair dryer, telephone and a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<ul>
<li>Twin room (A2): sleeps 2 people (22m²)</li>
<li>Family room (B4): sleeps 3-4 people (35-40m²). Additional sofa bed (suitable for 1-2 children up to 12 years) (on request)</li>
<li>Superior family room (C4): sleeps 3-4 people (40m²). Additional sofa bed (suitable for 1-2 children up to 12 years) or twin beds on mezzanine level (on request)</li>
<li>Junior suite (D4): sleeps 3-4 people (40m²). Additional sofa bed (suitable for 1-2 children up to 12 years) &amp; bath (on request)</li>
<li>Single room (F1): available (15m²) for sole occupancy (on request). Single rooms do not have a balcony</li>
</ul>
<p>All rooms take a cot.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
